title: 2018 Suwon JS Cup
text: The 2018 Suwon JS Cup is an international <a href="association%20football">football</a> friendly tournament. The tournament was used to prepare the host organisers for the <a href="2018%20AFC%20U-19%20Championship">2018 AFC U-19 Championship</a> in <a href="South%20Korea">South Korea</a>.
